title: rule breakers
comment: This refers to those who are breaking quarantine to, for example, go to the beach or other gatherings in other areas.

title: for myself
comment: I always get anxious when these events happen, leading to feeling false symptoms, and panic attacks.

title: for my family
comment: My family, specifically my parents and grandparents, are some of the ones who are specifically at risk or coronavirus, which makes me very worried.

title: cutural shift
comment: There is a change in culture, and I believe this to be both a good and bad thing. Mostly regarding technology and how people treat it, and the possibilities it brings us.
